It's time to <A href="/exhibitors/register/default.asp">register your booth staff and top 10 buyers</A>. Register by December 7, 2011, to have your badges mailed to you.<BR><BR> Questions? Contact International CES Exhibitor Registration Customer Service at 866-233-7968 or <A href="mailto:exhreg@CE.org">exhreg@CE.org</A>.<BR><br />
